This projet contains the SocialMediaClient Library that you might want to drag and drop to your personal project in order to connect your app to your favourites social media clients!\
\
This Library will work for both the iPhone and iPad by displaying the login windows as a classic full-screen modal view controller for the iPhone and as a sheet modal view controller for the iPad.\
\
At the moment, the Library supports the following clients:\
- Facebook\
- Twitter\
- Flickr\
\
In the near future, it could also includes:\
- Last.fm\
- LinkedIn\
(- Foursquare)\
\
\
In order to use it, you need to create accounts and get API keys for the following clients.\
You then need to replace the keys in DDSocialNetworkClient.h\
\
\
\
Then, to use the library in your project simply drag and drop the SocialMediaClient Library folder.\
\
In order for your project to compile after adding the SocialMediaClient library, you have to add the following frameworks:\
- CFNetwork\
- SystemConfiguration\
- MobileCoreServices\
- CoreGraphics\
- Security\
- libz.1.2.3.dylib\
- CoreLocation\
\
